original_title: Richmond: St. Pauls Avenue - Grant Street
text:
St. Pauls Avenue, west side, twenty-five feet north of Grant Street. Beers's 1874 map shows the house to have belonged to one named France.

November, 1919

P. L. Sperr

original_title: Richmond: Grant Street - St. Paul's Avenue
text:
Grant Street, at the S. E. corner of St. Paul's Avenue, showing Public School No. 15.

September 9, 1937

P. L. Sperr
